<div style="font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', serif; color: #1b1b18; line-height: 1.6;">
    <h2>Reset your FurHope password</h2>
    <p>Hello {{ user.firstName ?: user.email }},</p>
    <p>We received a request to reset your password. Use the button below to choose a new one.</p>
    <p style="margin: 24px 0;">
        <a href="{{ resetUrl }}" style="display: inline-block; padding: 12px 20px; border-radius: 999px; background: #cf6a32; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 700;">Reset my password</a>
    </p>
    <p>This link expires in {{ expiresInMinutes }} minutes.</p>
    <p>If you did not request this change, you can ignore this email.</p>
</div>
